dct_title_s: Montenegro city graphic 1:20,000. Podgorica. Series M903
dct_description_sm: Alternate title: Podgorica. Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 20 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. This sheet falls within NK 34-04, 1501A, 1:250,000 and 2979 IV, M709, 1:50,000. Coordinate conversion WGS 84 to ED 50. "Map information as of 1993." Reprinted by NIMA. With a glossary.
